    "name": "Kissmanga - Image Width Normalizer",
    "description": "Normalizes all manga images to a certain width (can be chosen in Advanced Style Settings).\r\nAdditional features: \r\n* Margin between manga pages can be chosen.\r\n* Optional zoom when hovering the mouse over an image (to read small text etc.).",
    "additionalInfo": "Version 1.0.3:\r\n* Zoom to browser-width when mouse hovers over image\r\n\r\nVersion 1.0.2:\r\n* Options for margin between manga pages added.\r\n\r\nVersion 1.0.1:\r\n* More width options.\r\n* 100% width is now really 100% (removed margin).\r\n* Now working with single page view as well.\r\n\r\n###################\r\n\r\nBrowsing kissmanga with your smartphone or tablet? Try out my \"Kissmanga - Mobile\" style :)",
